name: shit my mexican family has said - food edition #01
description:
i remember being scared the first time i decided to eat a banana at night and see what happened. YOLO. 

one night i was chewing gum and watching a movie. my grandma sits down next to me and after a few minutes ask me if I know what they say about people who chew gum at night. I said I didn't and that's when she told me that.
